SpectroPipeR - logo export

SpectroPipeR_logo_export.Rd

SpectroPipeR - logo export

Usage

SpectroPipeR_logo_export(output_location = "")

Arguments

output_location

folder location where the SpectroPipeR logo should be copied

Value

copies the SpectroPipeR logo to the designated folder

Examples


SpectroPipeR_logo_export(output_location = "../SpectroPipeR_test_folder")
